# module: eng.sampling
# status: planned
# purpose: deterministic sample tables and design sweeps with units, constraints, seed policy, and reviewable metadata.
#
# Current implementation:
#   no native sampling module yet. Use typed CSV sample tables and schema
#   constraints.
#
# Planned helper vocabulary:
#   grid sample
#   latin_hypercube
#   random sample with seed
#   sample manifest
#
# Review contract:
#   parameter schema, ranges, seed, sample count, sample row hashes, and
#   diagnostics for duplicate or invalid case IDs.
#
# Non-goal:
#   random sampling without an explicit seed must not pass repro review.
